<title>USA: Dillard April same-store sales flat.</title>
<headline>Dillard April same-store sales flat.</headline>
<dateline>LITTLE ROCK, Ark. 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Percent change</p>
<p>		    1997	 1996	     Total     Same-Store</p>
<p>Month		 $426	 $411	+4.0	 nil</p>
<p>Year-to-date    $1,515     $1,453	+4.0	 nil</p>
<p>NOTE: Figures in millions except percentage.</p>
<p>    Month is ended	 May 3.</p>
<p>Full company name is Dillard Department Stores Inc</p>
<p>Note: Sales for the 27 days ended May 3 were $413 million compared to sales of $411 million for the similar period last year.  This is an increase of 1% overall.  The comparable stores decrease for the period was 3%.</p>
<p>The company said it is providing this information on a twenty-seven day basis to correspond to information which was released last month.</p>
